PrecisApproval of the appointment made by the Minister of Communications of PIERRE ISABELLE, of Hull, Quebec, as a member of the NATIONAL CAPITAL COMMISSION, to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, in the place of Nicole Moreault, whose term has expired.
